								Apps and Integrations
							</div>
							<p class="double_line">
								Streamline work by connecting Slack with other services like Google Drive, Office 365 and over 2,200 more.
							</p>
							<a href="#" class="icon icon_arrow click feat_link"></a>
						</div>

						<div class="youNeed_card">
							<span class="icon feat_icon" style="background-image: url('/svg/youNeed/workflow.svg')"></span>
